    "headline": "Omnicom Launches Acxiom Fan Graph to Give Brands a More Complete View of Sports Fandom",
    "summary": "Omnicom (NYSE: OMC) today announced the launch of Acxiom Fan Graph, a new sports marketing intelligence solution anchored by Real ID™. The platform unifies data signals across media, commerce, attendance, purchases, participation, and consumer identity into a privacy-compliant view of fandom, giving brands the competitive insight they need to connect with sports audiences.",
